            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> et Iu<lb break="no" n="2"/>noni <expan><abbr>Regin</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>et Marti Ex<lb break="no" n="4"/>albiovici <lb n="5"/>dis deab<expan><ex>us</ex><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>omnibus <lb n="7"/>et Genio loci <lb n="8"/>pro se et suis <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Melici<lb break="no" n="10"/>us Respec<lb break="no" n="11"/>tus miles <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VIII <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/>b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste gelblich weißer Übermalung. Z.7/8 stand zunächst nur GENIO / LOCI, dann korrigiert.</p>
            </div>
